Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.43,0:01:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利和米蘭達一行逃到邊境星域中心巴格休後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.87,0:01:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上試圖接觸當地反泰坦尼亞勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不… 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是長得有一點點像…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 方修利來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 大家好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.53,0:02:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我 你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一步吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不用看店了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聯絡員
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然出了點意外
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:02:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但從那邊可以逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿一心追捕提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜遍了整片不毛之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發現了提督的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一方面 對於哲力胥卿侵害主權的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休政府也進行了武力抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.23,0:03:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於進入了交戰狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.42,0:03:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1292,885)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}正直老人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦 等待指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.51,0:04:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願護罩能頂住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意 反擊要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部炮門瞄準 準備齊射
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護罩不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.51,0:05:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 一鼓作氣打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是巴格休的軍艦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法識別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.83,0:05:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.87,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四艘交互封住對方退路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李博士 我們中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 上升
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 退路被封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 強行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炮門全開 全炮齊射
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各艦還擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經是烏合之眾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蘭達 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.43,0:07:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能迫降嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來大家都沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}伊文·卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イブン・カシム
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是伊文·卡西姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.18,0:08:33.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔任醫師 姑且算是首領
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客套話就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓我帶你們回基地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正直老人號還能用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 李？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 還是放棄正直老人號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外表可以修復
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但已經承受不了亞空間飛行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它還能撐下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很戀戀不捨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:09:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對艦長來說 就像和多年老友生離死別一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但接下來要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.61,0:10:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買新船需要好大一筆錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世態炎涼 若沒有錢的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務就是想辦法籌錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.55,0:10:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你就只會籌錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得倒輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.82,0:10:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要人抱怨的話 比你能說的有得是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休政府仍然沒有行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:59.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有多久到達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時七分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}巴格休軍司令本部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルガシュ軍司令本部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有緊急聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.87,0:11:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封鎖線被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(534,923)\fad(500,500)}伊克少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(534,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イルク少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1410,923)\fad(500,500)}托比爾少將
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1410,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}トゥルビル少将
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骯髒的鼠輩們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我親手把他們碎屍萬段
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挫骨揚沙！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請恕臣斗膽一言
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.07,0:11:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對付這種鼠輩 沒必要勞閣下親征…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.44,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下乃是泰坦尼亞的重臣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請自重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.89,0:12:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是杞人憂天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.61,0:12:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 我不會重蹈亞瑟斯的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.72,0:12:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這裡是塔魯哈利沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和宇宙戰不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.45,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在地面戰中 可能會被鼠輩反咬一口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到親手抓住方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一舉掃滅周圍的害蟲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情都無法平復
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個避免地面戰的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投下低周波炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活埋方修利一行的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:13:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利必須由我生擒 不要多說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 請恕屬下多言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在塔魯哈利沙漠地下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有巨大的洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在化為天然要塞的地下戰壕裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏有多達三千名反泰坦尼亞勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來哲力胥·泰坦尼亞本人終於登場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好驚人的數量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵力有我方的數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 數十倍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怕什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.73,0:14:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥親自來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不正是個好機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傻大個要是躲在天城的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倒也無計可施
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次對方主動闖進了我們的射程範圍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位姑娘真要強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,923)\fad(500,500)}雪拉芬·庫帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(780,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}セラフィン・クーパーズ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪拉芬·庫帕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我雪拉就好 但不要叫我姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:24.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和要強的女生還真有緣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是對方先來搭腔的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為泰坦尼亞喜歡恃強淩弱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大象一動 難免會踩死小螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.11,0:14:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小螞蟻也不是為被大象踩死而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我中意妳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不是為被泰坦尼亞趕來趕去而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只要想個辦法 把巨象哲力胥放倒就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻對大象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若他還執著於生擒我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.65,0:15:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就有反擊的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓對方稱心如意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬧到這個地步 巴格休軍不會袖手旁觀的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.12,0:15:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早有安排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現的是哲力胥·泰坦尼亞公爵的艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 巡視艇前去確認情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞的特務艦在巴格休境內動武了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無可爭辯的事實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還突破了封鎖線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以大艦隊大肆入侵…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命正規軍抓緊準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.98,0:15:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警戒態勢LV4
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.57,0:16:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休的巡視艇接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巡視艇要求通信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問如何處置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別理他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方繼續要求通信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴格休巡視艇 進入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.76,0:16:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.74,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但對方接到了巴格休政府的正式命令
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為執行公務而來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.84,0:16:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若開火的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等於向對方宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚要和巴格休政府做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.41,0:16:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們有膽量和泰坦尼亞全面對抗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得你是軍校出身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.72,0:17:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍校會從戰鬥形式開始傳授
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但古人說得好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.60,0:17:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥要先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.01,0:17:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 最初是警告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一發不准打中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方沒有回信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是旁若無人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方遭到攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上後退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急聯絡我軍司令本部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只被雷射擦肩而過就慌忙逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:18:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦交上手 我就是無敵的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於開始了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.38,0:18:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現正直老人號
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投到屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從受損程度看來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計對方棄船了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 殺雞儆猴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.31,0:21:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該採取下一步行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣等下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會在漆黑的地下東躲西藏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究會被追上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.68,0:21:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在天上還好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死在漆黑的地下確實讓人心有不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和方修利不同 我們沒必要留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們就算投降也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.42,0:21:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂窮鼠咬貓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就像被逼到沙子裡的老鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿之所以想要活捉方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既不是出於仁慈之心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.60,0:22:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是要把他告上法庭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是為了讓母親泰莉莎親手為亞瑟斯報仇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把提督折磨致死
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.87,0:22:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說哲力胥閣下發現方修利的老巢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.80,0:22:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.51,0:22:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.69,0:22:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼 我有種不祥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.12,0:22:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決戰之時已經逼近了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於把方修利的腿腳打斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利 你已經動彈不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.16,0:24:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要當場活捉你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(648,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}熱沙的激鬥


